Photography: Ana Isabel de Fontes Correia.
Twitter: @AnaIsabel_Photo
Trace - WoW #7479

“With the buzz of technology and the metaverse ever moving, sometimes all one needs to do is sit down, lay back and watch as the clouds go by. Count the unlimited shining stars, whisper wishes to the moon and connect with yourself. Touch the power of your heart chakra, listen to its beating… You are alive! Gratitude. Alignment. You are at peace and in harmony with nature. One with the Universe.” 
-- Trace, after the heist, 2.2.2222
